Camoflage::

She wiped her optics and saw several bots standing around her. Being 
spooked a bit, she transformed into fox pup mode and back to bot 
mode. "Uh, I'm not in trouble am I?" she said sniffling a bit. She 
looked up at the reptile and grinned a bit. "Hi, what kind of bot are 
you?"  She looked at Malice, "Whoah, I never met you before."  She 
looked at the other two bots and smiled. "Hi. I'm Camoflage. At least 
that's what Blackfang called me a long time ago. What's all your 
names?' she said trying to cheer up a bit.
